    "en": {
      "title": "Jagath, Chairman of the Petition Council",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Member of Parliament Mr. Jagath Pushpakumara was again appointed as the Chairman of the Committee on Public Petitions in the third session of the Ninth Parliament.",
        "The other members of the committee are Imtiaz Bakir Makar, Gamini Valeboda, Pyankara Jayaratne, Dilip Vedaarachchi, Vadivel Suresh, S. Vyalendran, Ashoka Priyantha, Arvind Kumar, Geetha Samanmalee Kumarasinghe, B. Y. G. Ratnasekara, Sarathy Dushmantha, Govindan Karunakaram, Jayantha Katagoda, Mohammad Mussammil, Thushara Indunil Amarasena, Velu Kumar, Varuna Liyanage, U. K. Sumit Udukumbura, Mayadunna Chinthaka Amal, Nipuna Ranawaka and Rajika Wickramasinghe were appointed."
      ],
